syntax (we are considering possibly adding this in a subsequent
release).  For examples of the basics of datatypes in Cedille, see
â€˜language-overview/datatypes.cedâ€™, and for an example of histomorphic
recursion see â€˜language-overview/cov-pattern-matching.cedâ€™.

